  "text": "The results also revealed that combined effects of morin + rutin and quercetin in combination with the antibiotics were additive (FICI <1). However, relationships between quercetin + morin + rutin and CEPH, IMP, CET and ME were synergistic (FICI ≤ 0.5). While Q + M + R with AMP and AMO showed additive effect (FICI <1). These results are in in conformity with earlier findings where quercetin was found to be synergistic with minocycline, fusidic acid and rifampicin [CITATION_1] .",
